{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1492538, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "啥是连笔字", "timestamp": 1618975394, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492546, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "主要是觉得不专门找到一种参考字体的话想不到那么连会好看", "timestamp": 1618975419, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492560, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": 1492538, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 行书？多个笔划连写在一起，不是像宋体那样一笔一划都是分开的", "timestamp": 1618975478, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492583, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": 1492560, "tag": null, "text": "买了本行楷字帖照着描, 渐渐就知道一些练笔要怎么处理了", "timestamp": 1618975668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492589, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": 1492583, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: Bob说的对，不管怎么说都应该从楷书练起", "timestamp": 1618975695, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492591, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": 1492560, "tag": null, "text": "不过基础不牢, 只会练笔没有任何间架结构, 就特别丑呜呜呜", "timestamp": 1618975696, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492595, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": 1492546, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 找行楷字帖临摹，一天半小时，一个月见效，三个月就比一般人好看了。沈鸿根，田英章都可以。主要是把笔顺感觉找出来，剩下的就是整理字和字之间的关系。一点都不难", "timestamp": 1618975702, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492604, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": 1492595, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 或者可以找古代的小楷字帖临摹，效果也是很显著的，cz之前是练的董其昌来着", "timestamp": 1618975765, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492605, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1936, "w": 2581}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1618975768, "type": "image", "url": "45/452ggqmr5imu4v3mzokr4jiwunqdnxoi.jpeg"}, {"cid": 1492607, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "bcd是对的，楷体是根基", "timestamp": 1618975787, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492609, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不要用那些带凹坑的，最好是有图示行笔顺序的。比如“有”，就是先写丿再写横\n", "timestamp": 1618975804, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492616, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建议买字帖临摹", "timestamp": 1618975838, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492736, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我以前是模仿老师的板书自己做笔记的时候练起来的，写字帖可能容易坚持不下来", "timestamp": 1618976643, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492760, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢大家！dz其实小时候练过楷体，有些法则还依稀记得，但感觉有些字还是需要单独找些连笔的法则。很长时间一直用电脑不写字，手都生疏了，前两天写字被自己丑哭了", "timestamp": 1618976793, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492788, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我是初中到高一都在写字帖 先写楷书 基础有了再写行楷", "timestamp": 1618976992, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492793, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "练一段时间就能写的挺好看啦", "timestamp": 1618977036, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492797, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不过大学不一定有时间ww）", "timestamp": 1618977050, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1492899, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 293618, "reply_to": 1492760, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 学书法就会了", "timestamp": 1618977573, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 293618, "reply": 18, "tag": null, "text": "好奇写连笔字好看的大家都是怎么做到的\n从某一时间段开始照着某种字体慢慢练的吗", "timestamp": 1618975339, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1618977570, "url": "", "vote": {}}}